parameters:
Teacher: "You're such a kind child. I wish I could make Saionji-kun
drink a decoction of your nail dirt. Hahahaha!"
01_カレンA_怒り
Karen: "What are you doing in my classroom, Morisaki!"
Yui: "What do you mean? I'm not doing anything special..."
01_カレンA_怒り

Karen: "You must have come to laugh at me! You really have a nasty
personality."
Yui: "Huh? What's gotten into you all of a sudden...?"

Karen: "Hah! Why are you playing dumb? It's your fault I'm in this
mess!"

Karen: "You must have whispered something to the principal. Just you
watch, I'll definitely get back at you for this!"
01_優衣_はぁ
Yui: "What on earth is going on...?"
Yui: "Saionji-san seemed angry, did something happen?"
Teacher: "Morisaki, huh..."
Teacher: "Actually..."

Teacher: "You know about the emergency meeting we had with the
teachers the other day, right?"

Teacher: "At that time, there was an agenda about the emergency
evacuation site in case we were attacked by Zaidarg-G..."

Teacher: "It was decided that the sports field would be used as the
emergency evacuation site."

Teacher: "And on the principal's suggestion, it was also decided to
build an evacuation facility on the sports field."
Teacher: "So for the time being, the sports field is off-limits..."

Teacher: "You see, Saionji-kun is in the track and field club. He
feels like his place has been taken away."
Yui: "Is that so? But it seemed like he was angry with me..."
Teacher: "Ah, that's because..."

Teacher: "Actually, besides the sports field, the gymnasium was also a
candidate for the evacuation site, but the principal stubbornly
insisted that the gymnasium was not an option."

Teacher: "You know, you're the ace of the karate club and you're even
in sight of winning the national tournament."

Teacher: "Saionji-kun thinks that the principal decided on the sports
field to avoid taking away your practice area."
Yui: "I see, so that's what it was."
Teacher: "Sorry. You got caught in the crossfire."
01_優衣_デフォルトA

Yui: "Please don't worry about it. I understand how Saionji-san feels
since he can't do club activities."

Teacher: "You're a kind person. I wish I could make Saionji-kun drink
a decoction of your nail dirt. Hahaha!"
実績 11
A
